name: Donald Taulbee
text:
Phoned in two orders at the same time
Picked up order when I arrived and waited 20 minutes for the other order. Got home and discovered I only got a 2 piece when I paid for a 4 piece. Done with this place.

name: Crystal johnson
text: This pizza was right outta of the oven delicious!

text: Great food and good prices. I’ll always be a regular here
